OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FNine rioters have been sentenced to a
OL,7,Ftotal of 48 years for their
OL,8,Finvolvement in unrest that took place
OL,9,Fin the Ely area of Cardiff in 2023.
OL,11,FAshton O'Dare, 28, Lee Robinson, 39,
OL,12,FMichaela Gonzalez, 37, Jordan
OL,13,FBratcher, 27, Tyler Stapleton, 26,
OL,14,FHarvey James 20, McKenzie Pring, 21,
OL,15,FJaydon Baston, 21, Kieron Beccano, 38,
OL,16,Fand Luke Williams, 32, were all
OL,17,Fsentenced at Cardiff Crown Court on
OL,18,FWednesday (17 June).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FTwenty more rioters will be sentenced
OL,7,Fover the next two days and another 10
OL,8,Fdefendants were previously sentenced
OL,9,Fin the youth court.
OL,11,FThe trouble started on the evening of
OL,12,F22 May 2023. Hours earlier, Kyrees
OL,13,FSullivan (16) and Harvey Evans (15)
OL,14,Fhad died after losing control of the e-
OL,15,Fbike they were travelling on, and
OL,16,Fcrashing.
OL,18,FThe court heard that "rumours" began
OL,19,Fcirculating "as to the cause of the
OL,20,Fcrash", with the police being blamed
OL,21,Ffor what happened.
OL,26,@zD@VOUzD@^O]{D@MOU|D@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FHostility escalated rapidly and it
OL,7,Fwasn't long before the police were
OL,8,F"confronted by a riot".
OL,10,FOfficers were vastly outnumbered by
OL,11,Fthe crowd but formed a line on Stanway
OL,12,FRoad, near to the scene of the crash.
OL,14,FThere they were subjected to verbal
OL,15,Fabuse and later a rain of missiles
OL,16,Fthrown by the crowd.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
