OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FThe court heard these took "all shapes
OL,7,Fand sizes, including bricks, concrete
OL,8,Fblocks, plaster, broken ceramic tiles,
OL,9,Fbottles, doors, drain covers, paint,
OL,10,Fmicrowaves, anything that could be
OL,11,Fthrown".
OL,13,FThe courtroom was shown a video of a
OL,14,Fpetrol bomb being hurled, which
OL,15,Fexploded over PC Zoe Lea - setting her
OL,16,Falight.
OL,18,FIn written testimony, the officer
OL,19,Fdescribed the experience as
OL,20,F"petrifying", Her protective clothing
OL,21,Fprotected her from serious harm.
OL,26,@nD@\OU|D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FFireworks were also launched at the
OL,7,Fpolice, who described "laughter and
OL,8,Fcheering" from the crowd when an
OL,9,Fofficer was visibly struck.
OL,11,FShouts of "aim for the legs" were
OL,12,Fheard, as rioters sought to inflict
OL,13,Finjuries on the police cordon.
OL,15,FIn all, 31 officers and one civilian
OL,16,Fwere hurt in the disorder. Injuries
OL,17,Fincluded a broken foot, hearing loss
OL,18,Fand concussion.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@IO]sD@KOUsD@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
