OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FOne officer described how he had
OL,7,Fsuffered a "complete psychological
OL,8,Fbreakdown" after the incident, which
OL,9,Fled to him leaving the police force.
OL,11,FThere was also substantial damage to
OL,12,Fproperty. Four cars "were burnt out
OL,13,Fcompletely", the court heard while 10
OL,14,Fothers were damaged.
OL,16,FThe repair bill faced by the council
OL,17,Fcame to #28,515 - including repairs to
OL,18,Fstreetlights and the road surface.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@JO]tD@UOUuD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
