OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FThe damage was such that when a two-
OL,7,Fyear-old child had a medical emergency
OL,8,Fin the early hours following the riot,
OL,9,Fthe ambulance could not get down the
OL,10,Froad and police medics had to assist.
OL,12,FThe court was told the total cost of
OL,13,Fthe trouble to South Wales Police was
OL,14,F"in excess of #1 million".
OL,16,FAt one point during sentencing, Judge
OL,17,FTracey Lloyd-Clarke ordered the
OL,18,Fcourtroom to be cleared after shouting
OL,19,Ffrom the public gallery.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
