OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FSentencing Ashton O'Dare to six years
OL,7,Fand six months in prison, the judge
OL,8,Ftold the 28-year-old that he had been
OL,9,F"instrumental" in starting the riot,
OL,10,F"whipping up the crowd" and "actively
OL,11,Fencouraging trouble".
OL,13,FLee Robinson threatened to kill one
OL,14,Fofficer and called the police "the
OL,15,Fbiggest organised crime gang", before
OL,16,Flater returning to film the riot. He
OL,17,Fwas also sentenced to six years and
OL,18,Fsix months.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@NO]rD@AOUrD@WO]rD@]OUvD@_OUwD@
OL,26,A]O]
