PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FMichaela Gonzalez, who threw a
OL,7,Fmissile, was jailed for five years and
OL,8,Ftwo months.
OL,10,FJordan Bratcher and Tyler Stapleton,
OL,11,Fwho both threw objects at police
OL,12,Flines, were sentenced to five years,
OL,13,Fsix months and four years, four months
OL,14,Frespectively.
OL,16,FHarvey James, who threw a rock at
OL,17,Fpolice and was 17 at the time of the
OL,18,Friot, received a 24-month community
OL,19,Forder.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
