FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FMcKenzie Pring, 21, was "one of the
OL,7,Ffirst to collect missiles" from a
OL,8,Fgarden in the area to throw at police.
OL,9,FHe was sentenced to four years in a
OL,10,Fyoung offenders institution.
OL,12,FJaydon Baston, who's also 21,
OL,13,Fcollected rubble from the road at the
OL,14,Fscene and was told he would have to
OL,15,Fserve four-and-a-half years in a young
OL,16,Foffenders institution.
OL,18,FKieron Beccano, 38, admitted he was in
OL,19,Fthe middle of group throwing missiles
OL,20,Fat police and was sentenced to five-
OL,21,Fand-a-half years in prison.
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@ZO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
