OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FLuke Williams, 32, was sentenced to
OL,7,Fsix years in prison. Williams live-
OL,8,Fstreamed the riot on his phone and
OL,9,Fencouraged others to join in. He
OL,10,Fcheered when an officer was injured
OL,11,Fand said they should be "euthanised".
OL,13,FDuring her sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,14,FLloyd-Clarke commended the "composure"
OL,15,Fof police during a "truly terrifying
OL,16,Fand life-threatening situation".
OL,18,FLast year, the police watchdog found
OL,19,F"no indication of contact between the
OL,20,Fpolice vehicle and the boys' e-bike"
OL,21,Fbefore the collision.
OL,26,@sD@YOUvD@\OUvD@fO]wD@TOU{D@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
