FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FThe IOPC said it had passed a file of
OL,7,Fevidence to the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService "to consider an offence of
OL,9,Fdangerous driving for the driver of a
OL,10,Fpolice van", but the CPS decided not
OL,11,Fto bring any criminal proceedings.
OL,13,FHowever, investigators said they had
OL,14,Fconcluded an officer had a case to
OL,15,Fanswer for gross misconduct "over the
OL,16,Faccuracy of accounts" provided after
OL,17,Fthe collision.
OL,26,@pD@IOUrD@KO]wD@]OUxD@UO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
