FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781780573
OL,3,CNine sentenced for a total of 48 years
OL,4,Cfor their part in Ely riots
OL,6,FThe IOPC also said the officer had a
OL,7,Fcase to answer, at the level of
OL,8,Fmisconduct, in relation to his driving
OL,9,Fand language he used in relation to
OL,10,Fthe boys at the collision scene.
OL,12,FAt the time of the announcement, the
OL,13,Fwatchdog said a second investigation
OL,14,Finto family complaints against South
OL,15,FWales was "close to concluding".
OL,26,@wD@KOU
